title: Spain 30 Year Bond Yield
description: Spain 30Y was 3.51 percent on Thursday November 10, according to over-the-counter interbank yield quotes for this government bond maturity. Historically, the Spain 30 Year Bond Yield reached an all time high of 7.62 in July of 2012. This page includes a chart with historical data for Spain 30 Year Bond Yield.
author: Tesoro Público
